ert</span>(chartgroup.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">CategoryCollection</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsFiltered</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
